dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Washington County, WI 2015
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Washington_Hydro_2015.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Washington_HydroLine_2015' and 'Washington_HydroPoly_2015'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
